Cathrine is the princess of the Light Realm, living alone in the castle. Well, not really alone, but without any family. Both her parents died, and on her eighteenth birthday she will become Queen. She puts her people as first priority, and is calm at all times. She is often serious, but from time to time allqws herself to have a little fun. To a passing observer she may seem dull, but those who know her know she can be fun, if you know how to get her mind off her people. Although she is a princess, she is not like Disney or anything, how she looks and acts is the least of her worries. She dislikes being addressed formally.\page ELLEN (LIGHT)\

