Susan, like the other wisdomforces, is a princess. But at first glance, you probably couldn't tell. Or second glance. She dresses like everyone else, acts like everyone else, speaks like everyone else, and basically acts as if she was just another person. She likes to have fun, but usually by herself. She has no real friends, nor does she want any. She dreads the coming of her 18th birthday, for her parents were killed when she was young. nevertheless, she cares for her people and will be a good ruler when the time comes. She dislikes the other forces, thinking they let heroism get to their head and work more for popularity than the good of the people.\page JANE (DARK)\

