It is rumoured that Boris no longer belongs to any realm. If this is true, then there is another unknown hero of the Dark Realm.\page 
\b BORIS
\b0 \
Boris was overcome by the power given to him, and seeks control of all three realms. He is the main threat to the realms. Although he holds power, he has mastered all three Forces and is able to use them expertly.\page 
\b the forces-
\b0 \
\
The Forces are the powers given off by the Equiforce. They are Power/Strength, Wisdom/Justice, and Courage/Bravery.\page POWER/STRENGTH\
\
Realm: Dark\
Color: Red/Pink\
Notes: Provides protection from fire, and, in some cases, provides control over the element.\page |!WISDOM/JUSTICE\
