\b cities and towns-
\b0 \
\
There are numerous cities and towns. The following are all I have named.\page BRADTON\
\
Will's hometown. A small village that's main feature is its ranch. Built on and around a small river.\page LEEGATE\
\
A larger village east of Bradton. Main feature: the many small shops dotting its streets.\page CROSSROAD\
\
A town where two rivers join and roads cross. Has a nice look and is a large trading center.}